---
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div
  class="mb-12 bg-black p-8 md:px-20 md:py-20 mt-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center">
  <h2 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">
    Submission Guidelines and Reviewing Process
  </h2>
  <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
    The workshop's extended abstract will be peer-reviewed by at least two PC members and one workshop organizer.
  </p>
  <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
    The maximum length for the extended abstract to the VisGames workshop is 2-6 pages including all images, acknowledgements, and references.
    We accept both double-blind (anonymized) and single-blind (not anonymized) submissions. 
  </p>
  <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
    Submissions must be made using the Computer Graphics Forum style, using the conference LaTeX template for workshops. 
    In the template you will find a proposed structure for the extended abstract.
  </p>
<div class="flex mt-5">
  <Link
    size="lg"
    style="outline"
    rel="noopener"
    href="/template.zip"
    class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
    target="_blank"
    href="javascript:void(0)"
    class="flex gap-1 ml-2 items-center justify-center cursor-not-allowed opacity-50"
    disabled>
    <Icon class="text-black w-8 h-8" name="bx:download" />
    VisGames Template
  </Link>
  <Link
    size="lg"
    style="outline"
    rel="noopener"
    target="_blank"
    href="javascript:void(0)"
    class="flex gap-1 ml-2 items-center justify-center cursor-not-allowed opacity-50"
    disabled>
    <Icon class="text-black w-8 h-8" name="bx:upload" />
    Submit to PCS
  </Link>
</div>
  <p class="text-white bold mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl">
    Select Society: Eurographics, Conference: EuroVis 2025, Track: EuroVis 2025 VisGames
  </p>
</div>
